text: Theo Piniau (born 8 June 1993) is a Papua New Guinean track and field athlete. At the 2016 Summer Olympics he competed in the Men's 200 m. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Papua New Guinean male sprinters Category:Olympic athletes of Papua New Guinea Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Commonwealth Games competitors for Papua New Guinea Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2014 Commonwealth Games Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2018 Commonwealth Games
